11:42.760 --> 11:46.652
Dank je, dank je.

11:46.760 --> 11:50.240
Kan je het daar leggen?

11:51.620 --> 11:52.542
Wat is dat?

11:52.650 --> 11:53.600
Dit is van Nederland.

11:53.660 --> 11:55.502
Wat is het?

11:55.610 --> 11:58.230
